<ecoSpold xmlns="http://www.EcoInvent.org/EcoSpold02" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.EcoInvent.org/EcoSpold02 ../../schemas/datasets/EcoSpold02.xsd http://www.EcoInvent.org/UsedUserMasterData ../../schemas/datasets/EcoSpold02UserMasterData.xsd">
  <childActivityDataset>
    <activityDescription>
      <activity specialActivityType="1" id="b1a16b7f-89f1-527b-a370-21ed9a2d6542" activityNameId="e36f0a0f-aba6-40de-900e-fa4ba434d825" parentActivityId="c8d84a17-4fda-4fbe-a3a6-30c66b82f682" inheritanceDepth="-1" type="1">
        <activityName xml:lang="en">market for coke</activityName>
        <includedActivitiesStart xml:lang="en">This activity starts at the gate of the activities that produce 'coke',  within the geography of China.</includedActivitiesStart>
        <includedActivitiesEnd xml:lang="en">This activity ends with the supply of 'coke',  to the consumers of this product. Transport is included. Product losses during transportation are assumed negligible and are therefore not included.</includedActivitiesEnd>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This is a market activity. Each market represents the consumption mix of a product in a given geography, connecting suppliers with consumers of the same product in the same geographical area. Markets group the producers and also the imports of the product (if relevant) within the same geographical area. They also account for transport to the consumer and for the losses during that process, when relevant.</text>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="1">This is the market for  'coke', in the China geography.</text>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="2">Transport from producers to consumers of this product in the geography covered by the market is included.</text>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="3">coke' is a fossil fuel with a calorific value of 28.6 MJ/kg. It is used as a solid fuel and is sourced from hard coal coke furnaces. Its main applications are in the following sectors: industrial fuel.</text>
        </generalComment>
      </activity>
      <classification classificationId="3aa0f2c5-1d26-4f98-8c2c-7406d4b7f2ae">
        <classificationSystem xml:lang="en">ISIC rev.4 ecoinvent</classificationSystem>
        <classificationValue xml:lang="en">1910:Manufacture of coke oven products</classificationValue>
      </classification>
